omce upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who rested on a banana tree which was in the bank river.in the same foresrt there live a crocidile and her wife.one day crocidile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree. the kind herted monkey offered him some food . the crocidile came the next day for more fruits , as he loved them . as they pass by they both cecame good friend. 
